Usage: ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php

++Arguments WITH REQUIRED value
  -m, --message           A Message to display when the prompt is displayed

--Arguments WITH OPTIONAL value
  -n, --answersWithNo   An Optional Message to display No is chosen from the prompt

++Optional Arguments WITHOUT value
  -h, --help                Show this Usage Help Information

Examples:
[1]
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php -m "Would you like to exit?"
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php -m="Would you like to exit?" -n
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php -m "Would you like to exit?" -n="Well Hellllooo there!"
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php --message="How about this time?" -n "Whoot!"
  ./prompt_tool_skeleton.php --help